sources.title: The Sin of Lena Rivers
sources.description: A girl born out of wedlock must fight prejudice and jealousy to make her way in the upper-class world of Kentucky horse racing. One of the better Tiffany productions. Filmed before in 1914. Directed by Phil Rosen Released in 1932 Second release in 1938 a.k.a. "Lena Rivers" Complete print
